summary: time for a 2018 art summary! the year isn’t over yet but i made it regardless! overall it was a year of quality over quantity. i...
caption:
time for a 2018 art summary! the year isn’t over yet but i made it regardless!

overall it was a year of quality over quantity. i was very busy for most of the year and only came back home once every 2 weeks. but i think the things i made were very good. and while i still have ways to go i still feel very confident with my current skills.

it was also a year of some occasional experimentation. i started dabbling in backgrounds,  trying lineless art in the hard way learned how to use photoshop, made timelapse gifs and even learned embroidery. 

again this month is far from over but one of my big art goals™ for 2019 and onwards is to experiment more- with different backgrounds, art influences and coloring techniques. and above all make use of my free time which i now have less of.
